Resolute Fst Prods (RFP) Shares Declined While Steelhead Partners Decreased Stake by $507,320; Colony Cap (CLNY) Stake Maintained by Kazazian Asset Management Llc


					

						July 20, 2017 - By Adrian Erickson

Michael Johnston decreased its stake in Resolute Fst Prods Inc (RFP) by 2.55% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Steelhead Partners Llc sold 101,464 shares as the company’s stock declined 4.30% while stock markets rallied. The hedge fund run by Michael Johnston held 3.87M shares of the paper company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $20.71 million, down from 3.97M at the end of the previous reported quarter. Steelhead Partners Llc who had been investing in Resolute Fst Prods Inc for a number of months, seems to be less bullish one the $412.85 million market cap company. The stock increased 1.10% or $0.05 on July 20, reaching $4.6. About 74,340 shares traded. Resolute Forest Products Inc (NYSE:RFP) has declined 21.24% since July 20, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 37.94% the S&P500.
Kazazian Asset Management Llc increased its stake in Colony Cap Inc (CLNY) by 54.13% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Kazazian Asset Management Llc bought 34,700 shares as the company’s stock 0.00% . The institutional investor held 98,800 shares of the consumer services company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $2.00 million, up from 64,100 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Kazazian Asset Management Llc who had been investing in Colony Cap Inc for a number of months, seems to be bullish on the $ market cap company. It is 0.00% or $0 reaching $0 per share. It is down 0.00% since July 20, 2016 and is . It has underperformed by 16.70% the S&P500.







Investors sentiment decreased to 0.92 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.16, from 1.08 in 2016Q3. It dived, as 24 investors sold CLNY shares while 68 reduced holdings. 25 funds opened positions while 60 raised stakes. 108.28 million shares or 2.14% more from 106.01 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Kayne Anderson Advsrs Limited Partnership holds 0.01% or 43,200 shares in its portfolio. Morgan Stanley has invested 0.01% in Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY). Knott David M holds 1,000 shares or 0.01% of its portfolio. Aqr Cap Mngmt Ltd Liability Com reported 195,541 shares. Credit Suisse Ag accumulated 333,358 shares. Sei Invests Co has 1,858 shares for 0% of their portfolio. 456 were reported by Us Commercial Bank De. Moreover, Thrivent Financial For Lutherans has 0% invested in Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY) for 21,250 shares. Strs Ohio invested in 34,600 shares. Boston holds 0.03% or 1.05 million shares. State Of New Jersey Common Pension Fund D has invested 0.02% in Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY). 240,300 are held by California Pub Employees Retirement. Fiera Cap Corp owns 38,805 shares for 0% of their portfolio. Nomura Asset Mgmt Ltd has invested 0% in Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY). Qs Invsts Limited Liability Corp has invested 0% in Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY).
More recent Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY) news were published by: Gurufocus.com which released: “Advisors Capital Management, LLC Buys Colony NorthStar Inc, WP Carey Inc …” on July 17, 2017. Also Forbes.com published the news titled: “Colony Capital (CLNY) Passes Through 8% Yield Mark” on December 15, 2016. Forbes.com‘s news article titled: “Colony Capital And NorthStar Complete Merger, Creating REIT With $58B Under …” with publication date: January 11, 2017 was also an interesting one.
Among 4 analysts covering Colony Financial (NYSE:CLNY), 3 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 1 Hold. Therefore 75% are positive. Colony Financial had 6 analyst reports since October 9, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The firm has “Outperform” rating given on Wednesday, October 5 by Wedbush. The firm has “Mkt Perform” rating given on Wednesday, January 4 by Keefe Bruyette & Woods. The company was maintained on Monday, November 16 by RBC Capital Markets. FBR Capital downgraded Colony Capital Inc (NYSE:CLNY) on Wednesday, March 2 to “Market Perform” rating. FBR Capital upgraded it to “Outperform” rating and $22 target in Monday, June 6 report.
More notable recent Resolute Forest Products Inc (NYSE:RFP) news were published by: Business.Financialpost.com which released: “$7 million Resolute Forest Products lawsuit against Greenpeace must continue …” on March 10, 2017, also Prnewswire.com with their article: “Resolute to Host Management Call to Discuss Second Quarter Results” published on July 17, 2017, Seekingalpha.com published: “Resolute Forest Product: Buy This Cyclical Commodity Company While It’s Out Of …” on March 07, 2017. More interesting news about Resolute Forest Products Inc (NYSE:RFP) were released by: Bna.com and their article: “Resolute Forest Can’t Escape Suit Over Retiree Health Benefits” published on March 03, 2017 as well as Seekingalpha.com‘s news article titled: “Resolute Forest Products Continues Its Turnaround Efforts” with publication date: May 08, 2017.
Among 5 analysts covering Resolute Forest Products (NYSE:RFP), 0 have Buy rating, 2 Sell and 3 Hold. Therefore 0 are positive. Resolute Forest Products had 8 analyst reports since October 21, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The firm earned “Hold” rating on Wednesday, April 19 by RBC Capital Markets. IBC upgraded the shares of RFP in report on Monday, June 5 to “Sector Perform” rating. The stock of Resolute Forest Products Inc (NYSE:RFP) earned “Reduce” rating by TD Securities on Friday, April 1. The company was downgraded on Thursday, January 5 by Scotia Capital. RBC Capital Markets upgraded it to “Outperform” rating and $7 target in Friday, February 5 report. The rating was downgraded by Dundee Securities to “Neutral” on Thursday, February 18. The rating was downgraded by RBC Capital Markets to “Sector Perform” on Monday, April 25.
Steelhead Partners Llc, which manages about $1.95B and $1.03B US Long portfolio, upped its stake in Advanced Micro Devices Inc (Prn) by 17.00M shares to 26.00 million shares, valued at $41.05M in 2016Q4, according to the filing. It also increased its holding in Webmd Health Corp (Prn) by 1.50 million shares in the quarter, for a total of 30.40M shares, and has risen its stake in Workday Inc (Prn). 
Analysts await Resolute Forest Products Inc (NYSE:RFP) to report earnings on August, 3. 


